dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading. Includes illustrations of flags of the world and country information. Shows time zones and the relative times in each zone. At head of title: Global Mapping. "Map Data & Cartography © The XYZ Digital Map Company (www.xyzmaps.com)." © Global Mapping.
